    "en": {
      "title": "From today QR Fuel delivery in the system",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "National Fuel Permit (QR) for obtaining fuel. The coding system is implemented from today 26).",
        "Also, the system of providing fuel to the last digit of the vehicle number plate will continue till August 1st and after that it will be completely QR. He also said that only code system will be implemented. (a)"
